    • EmbeddedWallet

    Interface EmbeddedWalletAbstract Internal

    Abstract base class for embedded wallet implementations

    Remarks

    Provides a standard interface for embedded wallets (Privy, Dynamic, etc.) Can be used as a signer for smart wallets when the embedded wallet is an owner
